Name:           Yogurt
Version:        @tag
Synopsis:       A MUD client
Description:    A MUD client for Haskell. Features prioritized, regex-based hooks, variables, timers, logging, dynamic loading of Yogurt scripts and more.

Author:         Martijn van Steenbergen
Maintainer:     martijn@van.steenbergen.nl
Stability:      Experimental
