Category:       Network
Build-type:     Simple

Library
  Build-Depends:    base >= 4 && < 5, mtl, regex-posix, containers, time, old-locale, readline, network, process, syb, hint, unix
  Exposed-Modules:  Network.Yogurt, Network.Yogurt.Mud, Network.Yogurt.Utils, Network.Yogurt.Engine, Network.Yogurt.Session
